 newvalue‚Üêobject Limit oldvalue;minmax
‚çù Handle range-limitation of new spinner value, including optional wrapping
 minmax‚Üêobject ‚éïVGET‚äÇ'_range' (0 100) ‚ãÑ minmax‚Üêminmax[‚çãminmax] ‚çù What are our (normalized) limits?
 :If object ‚éïVGET‚äÇ'_wrap' 0 ‚çù If we're wrapping around, recompute new value
     :If oldvalue<minmax[1]
